          "text": "TRUE/FALSE statements about radial nerve is/are: 1. Branch of posterior cord 2. Nerve of extensor compament of forearm 3. Arise from C5 - T1 4. Anterior interosseous nerve is a branch of it 5. Supply skin of extensor compament",
